title: Nick Jonas, Rick Ross, Meek Mill added to Tidal concert
text:
Nick Jonas, rappers Rick Ross, Meek Mill, French Montana added to star-studded Tidal concert THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   09, 2015 - 2:46 pmLast Updated: October 09, 2015 - 2:46 pm   
People: 
Arts and entertainment (1849) 

NEW YORK — Nick Jonas and rappers Rick Ross, Meek Mill and French Montana have been added to the Tidal X concert in October, concert organizers announced Friday. 
Previously announced artists include Tidal-owners Beyonce and Jay-Z, as well as Prince, Nicki Minaj, Usher, Lil Wayne, Damian Marley, Thomas Rhett. 
The concert, "TIDAL X: 1020 Amplified by HTC," will be held at the Barclays Center in Brooklyn, New York, on Oct. 20 and will be available for livestream to all Tidal users. 
The music and video streaming platform has been struggling to compete with services like Spotify since it was launched this year.
